query:
UPDATE bookmarks
              SET
                modified_at = datetime(),
                url_id = (SELECT url_id FROM urls WHERE link = ?),
                title = ?,
                description = ?,
                website_title = ?,
                website_description = ?,
                unread = ?,
                shared = ?,
                notes = ?,
                import_properties = ?
              WHERE bookmark_id = ? AND user_id = ?
